For the convenient functionality of UCRM in Angola, we intend to create a plugin for integration of the
Multicaixa payment system with UCRM, in each billing email sent it sends the payment reference created 
by the Proxypay API and similarly when a payment with reference occurs created be sent to the event to 
settle the invoice or the amount paid
Proxypay doc https://developer.proxypay.co.ao/v2/?php#introduction
